<p>The magnitude of sensory impairment may vary in people of differing weig=
hts.<sup id=3D"cite_ref-22" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikip=
edia.org/wiki/Blood_alcohol_content#cite_note-22"><span class=3D"cite-brack=
et">[</span>21<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup> The <a href=
