ass=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>37<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></s=
up> is the <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Standard_drink#Definiti=
ons_in_various_countries" title=3D"Standard drink">most frequently used mea=
sure in many countries</a>. Examples:
</p>
